checkpoints/
*.pth
*.bin
*.ckpt
*.onnx

# Temporary data outputs (from split / data IO utilities such as [src/ppiris/splits/create_splits.py](src/ppiris/splits/create_splits.py) and [src/ppiris/training_and_inference/data_io.py](src/ppiris/training_and_inference/data_io.py))
data/
datasets/
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp

# Embedding cache (downloaded via fetch scripts in [src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_embeddings.py](src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_embeddings.py), [src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_esmc.py](src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_esmc.py), [src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_prostt5.py](src/ppiris/embeddings/fetch_prostt5.py))
emb_cache/
embeddings_raw/
*.npy
*.npz
*.h5

